title: THURSDAY - Antonio Brown's return 2020
itunes:title: THURSDAY - Antonio Brown's return 2020
description:
The 49ers getting some bad news on the eve of their Thursday night matchup with the Packers (0:08) as several key players were placed on the reserve/COVID-19 list. We'll preview the Seahawks and Bills game (1:22) as well as the Ravens and Colts (2:25). Hear from Ravens QB Lamar Jackson (2:51) as he talks about his struggles as of late. Antonio Brown (3:11) set to make his Buccaneers debut on Sunday night against the Saints as he talks about his relationship with Tom Brady. We have the latest on Christian McCaffrey's status (4:02) as he looks to return from an ankle injury. Lions quarterback Matthew Stafford's availability for Sunday in jeopardy (4:21) and GMFB has a couple big-time guests (4:57) lined up for today's show
